OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FTravellers are being urged not to go
OL,7,Fto Dubai International or Dubai World
OL,8,FCentral airports unless their airline
OL,9,Fhas confirmed their departure time
OL,11,FThe first Britons to return home since
OL,12,Ffighting began in the Middle East over
OL,13,Fthe weekend have arrived in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
