OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FThe first flight out of Dubai since
OL,7,FSaturday arrived at Heathrow last
OL,8,Fnight with another from Riyadh and Abu
OL,9,FDhabi landing on Tuesday morning. But
OL,10,Fairspace remains heavily restricted
OL,11,Fover the Gulf region, and thousands of
OL,12,FBritish nationals are still stranded
OL,13,Fand unable to leave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FPassengers arriving from Abu Dhabi at
OL,7,FHeathrow this morning told GMB there
OL,8,Fhad been "chaos" after they were given
OL,9,Fjust ten minutes' notice to leave for
OL,10,Fthe airport, following days of waiting
OL,11,Ffor travel updates after airspace over
OL,12,FGulf countries was closed as Iranian
OL,13,Fmissiles targeted the region.
OL,15,F"We went to the airport and it turns
OL,16,Fout the flight was operational. I
OL,17,Fthink we were the first departure to
OL,18,FEurope out of the Middle East," one
OL,19,Fpassenger said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FThey describe the "frightening" ordeal
OL,7,Fof hearing and seeing missiles raining
OL,8,Fdown as alerts went off on their
OL,9,Fphones.
OL,11,F"It's just been hell, but we're lucky,
OL,12,Fwe're lucky. We're looking forward to
OL,13,Fgetting home," one couple said.
OL,15,FAround 300,000 British Citizens are
OL,16,Fbelieved to be in Gulf countries
OL,17,Ftargeted by Iran, and 102,000 have
OL,18,Fregistered their presence within the
OL,19,Fregion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FRapid deployment teams are being sent
OL,7,Fto the region to assist British
OL,8,Fnationals on the ground.
OL,10,FThe majority of departures from the
OL,11,Fregion remain cancelled.
OL,13,FAirlines are trying to get more
OL,14,FBritish passengers back home, but they
OL,15,Fare operating what they call select
OL,16,Fflights as and when it is safe to do
OL,17,Fso. Airlines have told passengers not
OL,18,Fto go the airports in the Middle East,
OL,19,Fbut to wait to be contacted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FEmirates plans to operate two flights
OL,7,Fto Heathrow and one each to Gatwick
OL,8,Fand Manchester.
OL,10,FAt least some of these flights will be
OL,11,Foperated by the airline's A380 jets,
OL,12,Fwhich can each carry up to 615
OL,13,Fpassengers depending on how they are
OL,14,Fconfigured.
OL,16,FCustomers with earlier bookings are
OL,17,Fbeing treated as a priority, and
OL,18,Fanyone who has been rebooked will be
OL,19,Fcontacted directly by the airline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FEtihad Airways has scheduled one
OL,7,Fflight from Abu Dhabi to Heathrow, and
OL,8,Fasked guests and members of the pubic
OL,9,Fnot to travel to the airport unless
OL,10,Fcontacted directly and provided with
OL,11,Fconfirmed ticket details.
OL,13,FThis is with a Boeing 787-10
OL,14,FDreamliner, which has 336 passenger
OL,15,Fseats.
OL,17,FQatar Airways ` which usually serves
OL,18,FHeathrow and Gatwick from Qatar ` said
OL,19,Fon Tuesday morning that its operations
OL,20,Fremain suspended because of the
OL,21,Fclosure of Qatari airspace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FAll British Airways flights to
OL,7,FHeathrow from Abu Dhabi, Amman,
OL,8,FBahrain, Doha and Dubai were cancelled
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, while Virgin Atlantic also
OL,10,Faxed a flight from Dubai to Heathrow.
OL,12,FSince the latest conflict between Iran
OL,13,Fand the US and its allies began on
OL,14,FSaturday, there have been widespread
OL,15,Fairspace closures in the Middle East,
OL,16,Fsparking major disruption to flights.
OL,18,FRoughly half a million passengers use
OL,19,Fairports in Dubai, Doha or Abu Dhabi a
OL,20,Fday, which are vital hubs for travel
OL,21,Fbetween Europe, Asia and Australia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,FIt is expected to take several days to
OL,7,Fclear the backlog of passengers
OL,8,Fwaiting to travel.
OL,10,FOn Monday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,11,FStarmer said the situation "may remain
OL,12,Fchallenging for some time" but that
OL,13,Fthe government was "looking at all
OL,14,Foptions to support our people".
OL,26,@sD@\OUtD@ZO]uD@TOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
