PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,F"And we're in close contact with the
OL,7,Ftravel industry and governments in the
OL,8,Fregion, including with our friends in
OL,9,Fthe UAE (United Arab Emirates), given
OL,10,Fthe concentration of British nationals
OL,11,Fin that country, and we're looking at
OL,12,Fall options to support our people.
OL,14,F"We want to ensure that they can
OL,15,Freturn home as swiftly and safely as
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
