FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772597016
OL,3,CFirst Brits return on Gulf evacuation
OL,4,Cflights as thousands remain stranded
OL,6,F"The FCDO (Foreign, Commonwealth &
OL,7,FDevelopment Office) phone lines are
OL,8,Fopen to provide consular support, and
OL,9,Fministers are available to meet MPs to
OL,10,Fdiscuss any individual cases."
OL,12,FBritish nationals are being advised to
OL,13,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,14,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,15,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,16,Fofficials expect to change rapidly.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
